{"storyMeta":{"storyReviewType":"NONE","storyId":"act16side_level_act16side_st02","storyGroup":"act16side","storySort":18,"storyDependence":"act16side_level_act16side_08_end","storyCanShow":1,"storyCode":"GA-ST-2","storyName":"鸢尾花","storyPic":null,"storyInfo":"夕阳正缓缓落下，重叠了他头顶的光环，宛若冠冕。她想起妈妈郑重说出的那个词——虽然并不十分明白——“殉道者”。","storyCanEnter":1,"storyTxt":"activities/act16side/level_act16side_st02","avgTag":"幕间","unLockType":"STAGE_CLEAR","costItemType":"NONE","costItemId":null,"costItemCount":0,"stageCount":1,"requiredStages":[{"stageId":"act16side_st02","minState":"PLAYED","maxState":"COMPLETE"}],"prev":16,"characters":["休露丝","尤卡坦","艾泽尔","莫斯提马","菲亚梅塔","薇尔丽芙","蕾缪安","奥伦","费德里科","塞茜莉亚","里凯莱","修士","安多恩","帕蒂亚","罗塞菈"]},"lines":[{"type":"HEADER","key":"title_test","skippable":"true","mode":"BLACK_MASK","text":"","id":0},{"type":"stopmusic","id":1},{"type":"Dialog","id":2},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":3},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":4},{"type":"Background","image":"26_g9_laterano_street","screenadapt":"coverall","id":5},{"type":"playMusic","intro":"$m_dia_street_intro","key":"$m_dia_street_loop","volume":"0.4","id":6,"musicid":0},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":7},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_262_1#2$1","name2":"avg_npc_263_1#1$1","fadetime":"1","id":8},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":9},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_262_1#2$1","name2":"avg_npc_263_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":10},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"休露丝","text":"我都要把这次来拉特兰当成一次度假了......没想到会发生这样的事。","id":11},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_262_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_263_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":12},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"休露丝","text":"尤卡坦，谢拉格也是有信仰的小国......为什么拉特兰可以这样？","id":13},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_262_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_263_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":14},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"尤卡坦","text":"拉特兰的影响力实在广泛得多......万国信使也是拉特兰教宗布局已久的安排。","id":15},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_262_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_263_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":16},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"尤卡坦","text":"谢拉格没有这样的基础。","id":17},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_262_1#2$1","name2":"avg_npc_263_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":18},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"休露丝","text":"哈......影响力，影响力，走出谢拉格才发现，影响力真是个麻烦的东西。","id":19},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_262_1#2$1","name2":"avg_npc_263_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":20},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"休露丝","text":"现在想想，也真亏恩希欧迪斯过去只靠自己在几个邻国间周旋。","id":21},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_262_1#2$1","name2":"avg_npc_263_1#4$1","focus":"2","id":22},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"尤卡坦","text":"如今，圣女大人的影响力也在逐步提升......我们有我们的优势。","id":23},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_262_1#9$1","name2":"avg_npc_263_1#4$1","focus":"1","id":24},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"休露丝","text":"嗯......可你觉得，拉特兰教宗说的那些，真能实现吗？","id":25},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_262_1#9$1","name2":"avg_npc_263_1#6$1","focus":"2","id":26},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"尤卡坦","text":"......我不知道。","id":27},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_262_1#9$1","name2":"avg_npc_263_1#6$1","focus":"2","id":28},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"尤卡坦","text":"我无法想象，各个国家保持更加紧密的联系，这片大地会是什么样子......这听起来像一个梦。也不知道是不是好梦。","id":29},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_262_1#9$1","name2":"avg_npc_263_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":30},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"尤卡坦","text":"但是那天的神迹......还有教宗的演讲，没有人能等闲视之。","id":31},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_262_1#9$1","name2":"avg_npc_263_1#6$1","focus":"2","id":32},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"尤卡坦","text":"拉特兰，果真是被眷顾之城......吗？","id":33},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_262_1#1$1","id":34},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"休露丝","text":"艾泽尔小哥，你们萨科塔怎么看这段时间的事？","id":35},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4036_forcer_1#1$1","id":36},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"艾泽尔","text":"嗯？啊......是，很大的冲击......","id":37},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_262_1#2$1","id":38},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"休露丝","text":"我想也是，听人说那口钟几千年没响过了。","id":39},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_262_1#1$1","id":40},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"休露丝","text":"拉特兰会怎么样？","id":41},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4036_forcer_1#1$1","id":42},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"艾泽尔","text":"......也许不会怎么样，以我对拉特兰人的了解......不，也许哪里都是一样。","id":43},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4036_forcer_1#1$1","id":44},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"艾泽尔","text":"即使发生了后世历史中举足轻重的大事......在当时当地，大家也许，都没什么实感。","id":45},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4036_forcer_1#1$1","id":46},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"艾泽尔","text":"但我们总会意识到变化正在发生，承担起属于自己的责任与使命。","id":47},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_262_1#3$1","id":48},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"休露丝","text":"......你还蛮有担当的嘛，小哥。","id":49},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_262_1#1$1","id":50},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"休露丝","text":"好了，就送到这里吧，接我们的车会开到这里来。","id":51},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_263_1#8$1","id":52},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"尤卡坦","text":"辛苦你了。","id":53},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4036_forcer_1#1$1","id":54},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"艾泽尔","text":"没事。薇尔丽芙枢机就在附近的医院，我直接去向她复命，很方便。","id":55},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_262_1#1$1","id":56},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"休露丝","text":"啊，说到那位枢机，替我向她道谢。","id":57},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4036_forcer_1#1$1","id":58},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"艾泽尔","text":"“您满意就好”——枢机是这么吩咐的。","id":59},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_262_1#1$1","id":60},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"休露丝","text":"真是滴水不漏......","id":61},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_262_1#3$1","id":62},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"休露丝","text":"对了，小哥，帮我和我丈夫拍张照吧。","id":63},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4036_forcer_1#1$1","id":64},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"艾泽尔","text":"好的。","id":65},{"type":"dialog","id":66},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_262_1#11$1","name2":"avg_npc_263_1#8$1","id":67},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":68},{"type":"playsound","key":"$skill_flash","id":69},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0.2","block":"true","id":70},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":71},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":72},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4036_forcer_1#1$1","id":73},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"艾泽尔","text":"这样就可以了吗？","id":74},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_262_1#11$1","id":75},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"休露丝","text":"摄影技术也不错，艾泽尔小哥。","id":76},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_263_1#8$1","id":77},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"尤卡坦","text":"谢谢。","id":78},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4036_forcer_1#1$1","id":79},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"艾泽尔","text":"两位不客气。","id":80},{"type":"Dialog","id":81},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_262_1#11$1","name2":"avg_npc_263_1#8$1","id":82},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":83},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","id":84},{"type":"character","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":85},{"type":"Delay","time":"2","id":86},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":87},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":88},{"type":"character","name":"avg_213_mostma_1#9$1","id":89},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莫斯提马","text":"菲亚梅塔，你有没有觉得自己的脚步特别沉重？","id":90},{"type":"character","name":"avg_300_phenxi_1#3$1","id":91},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"为什么？","id":92},{"type":"character","name":"avg_213_mostma_1#9$1","id":93},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莫斯提马","text":"教宗阁下讲了那样的话，你难道没有感受到肩上的重担？","id":94},{"type":"character","name":"avg_300_phenxi_1#1$1","id":95},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"所以？","id":96},{"type":"character","name":"avg_213_mostma_1#11$1","id":97},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莫斯提马","text":"所以我在认真考虑是不是该换一份工作了，太需要责任感的工作不太适合我。","id":98},{"type":"character","name":"avg_213_mostma_1#10$1","id":99},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莫斯提马","text":"我看你接替我就很合适。","id":100},{"type":"character","name":"avg_300_phenxi_1#6$1","id":101},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"做梦。","id":102},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4036_forcer_1#1$1","id":103},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"艾泽尔","text":"两位，下午好。","id":104},{"type":"character","name":"avg_213_mostma_1#5$1","id":105},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莫斯提马","text":"艾泽尔小哥，好久不见。","id":106},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4036_forcer_1#1$1","id":107},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"艾泽尔","text":"也就不到两周啦......","id":108},{"type":"character","name":"avg_300_phenxi_1#3$1","id":109},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"你......在执行任务？","id":110},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4036_forcer_1#1$1","id":111},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"艾泽尔","text":"薇尔丽芙枢机安排了一点事情，我正要去向她复命。","id":112},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4036_forcer_1#1$1","id":113},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"艾泽尔","text":"这是我在拉特兰城的最后一项任务了。","id":114},{"type":"character","name":"avg_213_mostma_1#10$1","id":115},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莫斯提马","text":"不错嘛，小哥，出去看过了就知道，拉特兰城蛮无聊的。","id":116},{"type":"character","name":"avg_213_mostma_1#10$1","id":117},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莫斯提马","text":"虽然外面没有那么多好吃的甜点，不过，我们生活的意义也不只是享受，对吧？","id":118},{"type":"character","name":"avg_300_phenxi_1#1$1","id":119},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"你要去找薇尔丽芙？她现在在哪？","id":120},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4036_forcer_1#1$1","id":121},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"艾泽尔","text":"司提望区中心医院。","id":122},{"type":"character","name":"avg_300_phenxi_1#1$1","id":123},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"......","id":124},{"type":"character","name":"avg_213_mostma_1#5$1","id":125},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莫斯提马","text":"走吧，艾泽尔小哥，我们同路。","id":126},{"type":"Dialog","id":127},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":128},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":129},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":130},{"type":"Character","id":131},{"type":"Background","image":"26_g7_laterano_ward","screenadapt":"showall","id":132},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":133},{"type":"playMusic","intro":"$dignified_intro","key":"$dignified_loop","volume":"0.4","id":134,"musicid":1},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":135},{"type":"Delay","time":"2","text":"","id":136},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_361_1#1$1","id":137},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"薇尔丽芙","text":"你决定了？","id":138},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_353_1#1$2","id":139},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"蕾缪安","text":"嗯，我决定了。","id":140},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_361_1#1$1","id":141},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"薇尔丽芙","text":"我以为你还要犹豫一段时间。","id":142},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_353_1#2$2","id":143},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"蕾缪安","text":"没什么......只是觉得，大家都迈出了下一步，我也不能再原地踏步了。","id":144},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_361_1#6$1","id":145},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"薇尔丽芙","text":"那我就不多问了。你能答应，我已经很高兴了。","id":146},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_361_1#6$1","id":147},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"薇尔丽芙","text":"现在这种时候，有你这样的人才加入，再好不过。","id":148},{"type":"dialog","id":149},{"type":"character","id":150},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","id":151},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4036_forcer_1#1$1","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":152},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":153},{"type":"character","id":154},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","id":155},{"type":"character","name":"avg_213_mostma_1#10$1","name2":"avg_300_phenxi_1#1$1","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":156},{"type":"delay","time":"3","id":157},{"type":"character","name":"avg_213_mostma_1#10$1","id":158},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莫斯提马","text":"就猜到你会在这里，薇尔丽芙。","id":159},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_361_1#4$1","id":160},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"薇尔丽芙","text":"你们怎么......","id":161},{"type":"character","name":"avg_300_phenxi_1#1$1","id":162},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"我们半路遇到了艾泽尔。","id":163},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4036_forcer_1#1$1","id":164},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"艾泽尔","text":"谢拉格的两位使者已经送达目的地了。","id":165},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_361_1#6$1","id":166},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"薇尔丽芙","text":"辛苦了。","id":167},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_361_1#6$1","id":168},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"薇尔丽芙","text":"别急着走，我来这里还有别的事，你跟我一起。","id":169},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4036_forcer_1#1$1","id":170},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"艾泽尔","text":"......是。","id":171},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_361_1#5$1","id":172},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"薇尔丽芙","text":"那么，蕾缪安，下周见。","id":173},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_353_1#9$2","id":174},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"蕾缪安","text":"下周见。","id":175},{"type":"dialog","id":176},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_361_1#5$1","id":177},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":178},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","id":179},{"type":"character","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":180},{"type":"Delay","time":"2","id":181},{"type":"character","name":"avg_300_phenxi_1#1$1","id":182},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"决定去七厅了吗，蕾缪安？","id":183},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_353_1#9$2","id":184},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"蕾缪安","text":"已经在做事了嘛。","id":185},{"type":"character","name":"avg_300_phenxi_1#1$1","id":186},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"......会议之后，去七厅会很辛苦吧。","id":187},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_353_1#10$2","id":188},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"蕾缪安","text":"不觉得七厅很适合我吗？","id":189},{"type":"character","name":"avg_300_phenxi_1#1$1","id":190},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"是倒是啦......","id":191},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_353_1#9$2","id":192},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"蕾缪安","text":"你们都走上了自己的路，我也该想想我能做的事啦。","id":193},{"type":"character","name":"avg_213_mostma_1#10$1","id":194},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莫斯提马","text":"我刚才还在和菲亚梅塔说，想辞了万国信使的工作。","id":195},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_353_1#1$2","id":196},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"蕾缪安","text":"怕麻烦了？","id":197},{"type":"character","name":"avg_213_mostma_1#9$1","id":198},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莫斯提马","text":"那老家伙......我已经看到麻烦越来越多的未来了。","id":199},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_353_1#9$2","id":200},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"蕾缪安","text":"跑不掉的哦，莫斯提马。你要归我直管了。","id":201},{"type":"character","name":"avg_213_mostma_1#4$1","id":202},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莫斯提马","text":"啊。","id":203},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_353_1#10$2","id":204},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"蕾缪安","text":"先帮我个小忙，把这封信带去给小乐。","id":205},{"type":"character","name":"avg_213_mostma_1#11$1","id":206},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莫斯提马","text":"......能拒绝吗？","id":207},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_353_1#7$2","id":208},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"蕾缪安","text":"不能。","id":209},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_353_1#10$2","id":210},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"蕾缪安","text":"而且你必须亲手交给她。","id":211},{"type":"character","name":"avg_213_mostma_1#11$1","id":212},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莫斯提马","text":"更想辞职了......","id":213},{"type":"character","name":"avg_300_phenxi_1#6$1","id":214},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"别说敷衍自己的话。","id":215},{"type":"character","name":"avg_213_mostma_1#11$1","id":216},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莫斯提马","text":"好严格啊，菲亚梅塔。","id":217},{"type":"character","name":"avg_300_phenxi_1#6$1","id":218},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"你不会放弃的。","id":219},{"type":"character","name":"avg_213_mostma_1#7$1","id":220},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莫斯提马","text":"这么肯定？","id":221},{"type":"character","name":"avg_300_phenxi_1#8$1","id":222},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"别装得像你不需要这份工作。","id":223},{"type":"character","name":"avg_300_phenxi_1#1$1","id":224},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"你也在找答案，不是吗？","id":225},{"type":"character","name":"avg_213_mostma_1#10$1","id":226},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莫斯提马","text":"我可不是安多恩......","id":227},{"type":"character","name":"avg_300_phenxi_1#1$1","id":228},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"没说你是。","id":229},{"type":"character","name":"avg_300_phenxi_1#1$1","id":230},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"但你还要选，对吗，关于你到底是谁。","id":231},{"type":"character","name":"avg_300_phenxi_1#8$1","id":232},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"要回答这样的问题......每个人都得走过足够长的路。","id":233},{"type":"character","name":"avg_213_mostma_1#10$1","id":234},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莫斯提马","text":"......","id":235},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_353_1#10$2","id":236},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"蕾缪安","text":"哎呀，莫斯提马，被理解的感觉怎么样？看来不需要光环也能理解你哦？","id":237},{"type":"character","name":"avg_213_mostma_1#9$1","id":238},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莫斯提马","text":"......那这就是我自己的路。你不该跟着我，菲亚梅塔。","id":239},{"type":"character","name":"avg_300_phenxi_1#2$1","id":240},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"少自大了，谁跟着你？只是恰好同路。","id":241},{"type":"character","name":"avg_300_phenxi_1#7$1","id":242},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"他的铳在我手上。","id":243},{"type":"character","name":"avg_300_phenxi_1#7$1","id":244},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"如果他真的还认为自己是一个萨科塔，他会来取回这把铳的。","id":245},{"type":"character","name":"avg_300_phenxi_1#7$1","id":246},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"到了那个时候，我会让他为自己做的事付出代价......！","id":247},{"type":"character","name":"avg_300_phenxi_1#1$1","id":248},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"你要做我的帮手。","id":249},{"type":"character","name":"avg_213_mostma_1#2$1","id":250},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莫斯提马","text":"......好吧。","id":251},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_353_1#9$2","id":252},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"蕾缪安","text":"说到这个，之前在城里抓到的迷途者，已经全部释放了哦。","id":253},{"type":"character","name":"avg_300_phenxi_1#3$1","id":254},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"......是教宗阁下的意思吗？","id":255},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_353_1#9$2","id":256},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"蕾缪安","text":"嗯哼。","id":257},{"type":"character","name":"avg_300_phenxi_1#8$1","id":258},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"教宗阁下的仁慈和我没关系。","id":259},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_353_1#10$2","id":260},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"蕾缪安","text":"......真是菲亚梅塔的风格啊。","id":261},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_353_1#9$2","id":262},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"蕾缪安","text":"另外，之后会让你走五厅的流程，用公证所的协议挂靠到罗德岛。","id":263},{"type":"character","name":"avg_300_phenxi_1#3$1","id":264},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"呃，莫斯提马和蕾缪乐兼职的那家医药公司......？","id":265},{"type":"character","name":"avg_300_phenxi_1#3$1","id":266},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"为什么？","id":267},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_353_1#10$2","id":268},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"蕾缪安","text":"薇尔丽芙希望和那家公司加深合作，你作为人选就很合适啊~","id":269},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_353_1#10$2","id":270},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"蕾缪安","text":"而且，就我所知，我们和那家公司的合作记录相当不错，应该能给你提供不少支持。","id":271},{"type":"character","name":"avg_300_phenxi_1#1$1","id":272},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"明白了。","id":273},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_353_1#9$2","id":274},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"蕾缪安","text":"然后然后，菲亚梅塔，还有一个超级好消息要告诉你！","id":275},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_353_1#10$2","id":276},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"蕾缪安","text":"现在，你竟然可以从三~个代号里！选一个，成为你下次的任务代号哦。","id":277},{"type":"character","name":"avg_300_phenxi_1#1$1","id":278},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"......说实在的，既然现在是你和我们对接，这个规则真的不能取消吗？","id":279},{"type":"character","name":"avg_300_phenxi_1#4$1","id":280},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"只是因为当时没有明确的监视这家伙的职位，才临时起了个名字......","id":281},{"type":"character","name":"avg_300_phenxi_1#2$1","id":282},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"我已经受够每个月都会变一次的职位名了！","id":283},{"type":"character","name":"avg_213_mostma_1#5$1","id":284},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莫斯提马","text":"微光守夜人你不是挺喜欢的吗，还说上面的品味总算变好了一些。","id":285},{"type":"character","name":"avg_300_phenxi_1#6$1","id":286},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"你给我闭嘴。","id":287},{"type":"character","name":"avg_213_mostma_1#10$1","id":288},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莫斯提马","text":"啊，这朵花真好看。","id":289},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_353_1#10$2","id":290},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"蕾缪安","text":"话是这样说......可事到如今，你职位名字的变化也已经成了一种规则了，就认命吧~","id":291},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_353_1#10$2","id":292},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"蕾缪安","text":"“虚空美食家”，“旷野飞行员”，“黎明破坏者”，选一个。","id":293},{"type":"character","name":"avg_300_phenxi_1#8$1","id":294},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"......“黎明破坏者”。","id":295},{"type":"character","name":"avg_213_mostma_1#5$1","id":296},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莫斯提马","text":"说真的，菲亚梅塔，你的品味挺好懂的。","id":297},{"type":"character","name":"avg_300_phenxi_1#2$1","id":298},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"你给我闭嘴！","id":299},{"type":"Dialog","id":300},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":301},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":302},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1","id":303},{"type":"Character","id":304},{"type":"Background","image":"26_g7_laterano_ward","screenadapt":"showall","id":305},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":306},{"type":"playMusic","intro":"$dignified_intro","key":"$dignified_loop","volume":"0.4","id":307,"musicid":2},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":308},{"type":"Delay","time":"2","text":"","id":309},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_355_1#10$1","id":310},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"奥伦","text":"嘶......","id":311},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_361_1#5$1","id":312},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"薇尔丽芙","text":"醒了？","id":313},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_355_1#8$1","id":314},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"奥伦","text":"......感觉我最近真的很倒霉。","id":315},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_361_1#5$1","id":316},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"薇尔丽芙","text":"怎么，嫌躺着不舒服？","id":317},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_355_1#2$1","id":318},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"奥伦","text":"不会，当我没说。","id":319},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_355_1#3$1","id":320},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"奥伦","text":"嗯？艾泽尔小哥也在？","id":321},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_361_1#6$1","id":322},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"薇尔丽芙","text":"我让他来看看，差点背叛拉特兰的人会有什么下场。","id":323},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4036_forcer_1#1$1","id":324},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"艾泽尔","text":"呃......","id":325},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_355_1#2$1","id":326},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"奥伦","text":"这么敲打年轻人也太过分了，薇尔丽芙。","id":327},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_361_1#5$1","id":328},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"薇尔丽芙","text":"我也是年轻人。","id":329},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_355_1#5$1","id":330},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"奥伦","text":"对不起。","id":331},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_361_1#2$1","id":332},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"薇尔丽芙","text":"你不再是万国信使了。","id":333},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_355_1#5$1","id":334},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"奥伦","text":"如果这就是代价......","id":335},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_361_1#6$1","id":336},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"薇尔丽芙","text":"但你仍然是我的部下。","id":337},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_355_1#10$1","id":338},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"奥伦","text":"那这代价还不小。","id":339},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_361_1#6$1","id":340},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"薇尔丽芙","text":"你向我夸下了海口，奥伦。那就让我看看，你在维多利亚都学到了什么。","id":341},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_355_1#2$1","id":342},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"奥伦","text":"......我是否可以认为，你需要我以我的方式行事？","id":343},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_361_1#6$1","id":344},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"薇尔丽芙","text":"现在，我可以回答你之前那个问题。","id":345},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_361_1#1$1","id":346},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"薇尔丽芙","text":"奥伦，我对于成为一个高尚的人没有兴趣。","id":347},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_361_1#1$1","id":348},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"薇尔丽芙","text":"但我并不讨厌为了高尚的人而付出努力。","id":349},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_355_1#1$1","id":350},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"奥伦","text":"这......我倒也不反对。","id":351},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4036_forcer_1#1$1","id":352},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"艾泽尔","text":"这些话也是说给我听的吗，枢机？","id":353},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_361_1#5$1","id":354},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"薇尔丽芙","text":"当然。","id":355},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_361_1#5$1","id":356},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"薇尔丽芙","text":"珍惜你和塞茜莉亚得到的机会。别让我知道，她会对拉特兰......有什么影响。","id":357},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4036_forcer_1#1$1","id":358},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"艾泽尔","text":"您......不希望塞茜莉亚再回到拉特兰？","id":359},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_361_1#6$1","id":360},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"薇尔丽芙","text":"如果我那么希望，为什么要花时间给那个孩子造一个户籍呢？","id":361},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_361_1#6$1","id":362},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"薇尔丽芙","text":"除了，啊，同情。更重要的当然是......她还有别样的价值，我愿意为这种价值而承担风险。","id":363},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4036_forcer_1#1$1","id":364},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"艾泽尔","text":"......","id":365},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_355_1#1$1","id":366},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"奥伦","text":"相信我，小哥，获得这种坦率的承诺对你只有好处。","id":367},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4036_forcer_1#1$1","id":368},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"艾泽尔","text":"我明白。","id":369},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_361_1#6$1","id":370},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"薇尔丽芙","text":"不用紧张。我只是在向你展现属于拉特兰的诚意，仅此而已。","id":371},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_361_1#6$1","id":372},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"薇尔丽芙","text":"若你和塞茜莉亚何时厌倦了旅行......你们还可以回到拉特兰。","id":373},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_361_1#6$1","id":374},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"薇尔丽芙","text":"拉特兰会给你们留一扇门。","id":375},{"type":"character","id":376},{"type":"dialog","id":377},{"type":"playsound","key":"$doorknockquite","id":378},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":379},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_361_1#5$1","id":380},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"薇尔丽芙","text":"请进。","id":381},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4036_forcer_1#1$1","id":382},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"艾泽尔","text":"费德里科前辈？","id":383},{"type":"character","name":"char_279_excu_4","id":384},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"枢机薇尔丽芙，这是前万国信使奥伦·亚吉奥拉斯近两年的出行记录报告。","id":385},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_361_1#6$1","id":386},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"薇尔丽芙","text":"辛苦你了，执行者费德里科。","id":387},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_355_1#2$1","id":388},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"奥伦","text":"呃......","id":389},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_361_1#5$1","id":390},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"薇尔丽芙","text":"以防万一。","id":391},{"type":"character","name":"char_279_excu_4","id":392},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"根据已有情报，推测执行者里凯莱可能是他的共犯，需要传讯里凯莱吗？","id":393},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_361_1#5$1","id":394},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"薇尔丽芙","text":"不用。他一定会说自己“被老同学蒙在鼓里”，对吧，奥伦？","id":395},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_355_1#5$1","id":396},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"奥伦","text":"......可怕的女人。","id":397},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_361_1#1$1","id":398},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"薇尔丽芙","text":"我不会追究里凯莱......暂时。","id":399},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_361_1#1$1","id":400},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"薇尔丽芙","text":"不过，之后我希望通过你和他聊一聊，没问题吧？","id":401},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_355_1#5$1","id":402},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"奥伦","text":"没有，完全没有。","id":403},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_361_1#6$1","id":404},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"薇尔丽芙","text":"目前对此二人的处置就是这样，执行者费德里科。","id":405},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_355_1#5$1","id":406},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"奥伦","text":"......","id":407},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_355_1#2$1","id":408},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"奥伦","text":"等等，费德里科。","id":409},{"type":"character","name":"char_279_excu_4","id":410},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"什么事？","id":411},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_355_1#2$1","id":412},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"奥伦","text":"我后来想到一件事。你从一本笔记的寥寥数语，要摸清那个和萨卡兹见面的女人是费莉亚，这不是件容易的事......","id":413},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_355_1#2$1","id":414},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"奥伦","text":"为什么那么执着？","id":415},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_355_1#2$1","id":416},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"奥伦","text":"你在找的究竟是谁？","id":417},{"type":"character","name":"char_279_excu_4","id":418},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"......阿尔图罗。","id":419},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_355_1#3$1","id":420},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"奥伦","text":"阿尔图罗......嗯？阿尔图罗？","id":421},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_361_1#4$1","id":422},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"薇尔丽芙","text":"就是那个通缉犯阿尔图罗？","id":423},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_355_1#3$1","id":424},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"奥伦","text":"......费德里科，你和阿尔图罗是什么关系？","id":425},{"type":"character","name":"char_279_excu_4#2","id":426},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"她是我的远亲。","id":427},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_355_1#4$1","id":428},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"奥伦","text":"......哈，哈哈哈哈哈！","id":429},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_355_1#1$1","id":430},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"奥伦","text":"说实在的，费德里科。","id":431},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_355_1#4$1","id":432},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"奥伦","text":"如果不是我现在站都站不稳，我真的想拉你去喝个酒。","id":433},{"type":"character","name":"char_279_excu_4","id":434},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"我没有空。","id":435},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_355_1#1$1","id":436},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"奥伦","text":"你会有的。因为我恰好在几年前......真的见到过那位比安多恩名气还要大得多的通缉犯，阿尔图罗小姐。","id":437},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_361_1#3$1","id":438},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"薇尔丽芙","text":"......","id":439},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_355_1#3$1","id":440},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"奥伦","text":"冷静！冷静！薇尔丽芙！！！","id":441},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_355_1#3$1","id":442},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"奥伦","text":"我不是主动找上阿尔图罗！只是正好碰上！","id":443},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_355_1#8$1","id":444},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"奥伦","text":"说真的，我自认算见多识广，但那段经历，即使是我也感到毛骨悚然......","id":445},{"type":"character","name":"char_279_excu_4#4","id":446},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"你在哪里见到她？","id":447},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_355_1#8$1","id":448},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"奥伦","text":"三年前，在莱塔尼亚。","id":449},{"type":"dialog","id":450},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":451},{"type":"character","id":452},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":453},{"type":"Background","image":"26_g5_laterano_chapelout","screenadapt":"coverall","id":454},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":455},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":456},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","id":457},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_352_1#5$1","name2":"avg_npc_372_1#10$1","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":458},{"type":"delay","time":"3","id":459},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_352_1#5$1","id":460},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞茜莉亚","text":"艾泽尔哥哥！","id":461},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4036_forcer_1#3$1","id":462},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"艾泽尔","text":"塞茜莉亚！","id":463},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4036_forcer_1#3$1","id":464},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"艾泽尔","text":"里凯莱前辈......","id":465},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_372_1#10$1","id":466},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"里凯莱","text":"各种手续都办好了，她现在可以自由离开拉特兰了。","id":467},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4036_forcer_1#8$1","id":468},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"艾泽尔","text":"谢谢你，里凯莱前辈。","id":469},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_372_1#10$1","id":470},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"里凯莱","text":"应该的。","id":471},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_372_1#1$1","id":472},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"里凯莱","text":"你知道自己接下来该去哪吧？","id":473},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4036_forcer_1#8$1","id":474},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"艾泽尔","text":"嗯......我们先去和费德里科前辈会合，去一家叫做罗德岛的公司挂靠一个合作协议。毕竟要在外面待很久......据说这样会方便很多。","id":475},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_372_1#1$1","id":476},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"里凯莱","text":"嗯，你记得就好，招呼我已经打过了。","id":477},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_372_1#1$1","id":478},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"里凯莱","text":"你仍然是公证所的执行者。不方便回来的时候，任务也会通过罗德岛发给你。","id":479},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_372_1#3$1","id":480},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"里凯莱","text":"我有预感，你和小塞茜莉亚的旅途会很顺利，说不定很快就能找到要找的人哦。","id":481},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_372_1#10$1","id":482},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"里凯莱","text":"我的预感一向很准。","id":483},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4036_forcer_1#8$1","id":484},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"艾泽尔","text":"......谢谢？","id":485},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_372_1#10$1","id":486},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"里凯莱","text":"那我就先走了，再见，小塞茜莉亚。","id":487},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_352_1#10$1","id":488},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞茜莉亚","text":"再见，里凯莱哥哥。","id":489},{"type":"character","id":490},{"type":"Dialog","id":491},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"里凯莱","text":"阿嚏！","id":492},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"里凯莱","text":"嘶......怎么忽然有种要倒霉的预感。","id":493},{"type":"character","id":494},{"type":"Dialog","id":495},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":496},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4036_forcer_1#1$1","id":497},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"艾泽尔","text":"里凯莱前辈也相当有个性啊。","id":498},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4036_forcer_1#3$1","id":499},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"艾泽尔","text":"咦，等等，他怎么知道我们在找......","id":500},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_352_1#5$1","id":501},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞茜莉亚","text":"艾泽尔哥哥，怎么了？","id":502},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4036_forcer_1#8$1","id":503},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"艾泽尔","text":"没事，塞茜莉亚。","id":504},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4036_forcer_1#8$1","id":505},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"艾泽尔","text":"还想......说点什么吗？","id":506},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_352_1#2$1","id":507},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞茜莉亚","text":"......","id":508},{"type":"dialog","id":509},{"type":"character","id":510},{"type":"Text","text":"女孩松开了年轻萨科塔的手，走入花田中央。","id":511},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_352_1#2$1","id":512},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞茜莉亚","text":"（我要离开拉特兰了，妈妈。）","id":513},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_352_1#2$1","id":514},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞茜莉亚","text":"（但不是逃走。）","id":515},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_352_1#2$1","id":516},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞茜莉亚","text":"（我会自己去找爸爸，会把你的话带给他。）","id":517},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_352_1#2$1","id":518},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞茜莉亚","text":"（我要用自己的眼睛看外面的世界......我要去找卡兹戴尔。）","id":519},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_352_1#11$1","id":520},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞茜莉亚","text":"（妈妈，我很幸福。过去、现在......）","id":521},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_352_1#11$1","id":522},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞茜莉亚","text":"（请看着我。）","id":523},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_352_1#10$1","id":524},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞茜莉亚","text":"修士姐姐，我可以摘一朵白色的花吗？","id":525},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_369_1#1$1","id":526},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"修士","text":"可以的，小妹妹。","id":527,"figure":"avg_npc_369_1#1$1"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_352_1#6$1","id":528},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞茜莉亚","text":"谢谢！","id":529,"figure":"avg_npc_369_1#1$1"},{"type":"dialog","id":530},{"type":"character","id":531},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":532},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4036_forcer_1#3$1","name2":"char_empty","id":533},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$rungeneral","volume":"1","id":534},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4036_forcer_1#3$1","name2":"avg_npc_352_1#6$1","enter2":"right","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":535},{"type":"delay","time":"3","id":536},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4036_forcer_1#3$1","name2":"avg_npc_352_1#6$1","focus":"1","id":537},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"艾泽尔","text":"塞茜莉亚要带走这朵花吗？","id":538,"figure":"avg_4036_forcer_1#3$1"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4036_forcer_1#3$1","name2":"avg_npc_352_1#6$1","focus":"2","id":539},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞茜莉亚","text":"嗯。","id":540,"figure":"avg_4036_forcer_1#3$1"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4036_forcer_1#8$1","name2":"avg_npc_352_1#6$1","focus":"1","id":541},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"艾泽尔","text":"鲜花可能保存不了太久......我帮你做成标本吧？","id":542,"figure":"avg_4036_forcer_1#3$1"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4036_forcer_1#8$1","name2":"avg_npc_352_1#10$1","focus":"2","id":543},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞茜莉亚","text":"嗯，请教教我，我也想学会自己做。","id":544,"figure":"avg_4036_forcer_1#3$1"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_352_1#10$1","id":545},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞茜莉亚","text":"谢谢你，艾泽尔哥哥。","id":546,"figure":"avg_4036_forcer_1#3$1"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4036_forcer_1#3$1","id":547},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"艾泽尔","text":"......嗯？","id":548,"figure":"avg_4036_forcer_1#3$1"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4036_forcer_1#8$1","id":549},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"艾泽尔","text":"塞茜莉亚，该说谢谢的是我。","id":550,"figure":"avg_4036_forcer_1#3$1"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_352_1#5$1","id":551},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞茜莉亚","text":"咦......那是......？","id":552,"figure":"avg_4036_forcer_1#3$1"},{"type":"Dialog","id":553},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":554},{"type":"character","id":555},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":556},{"type":"Background","image":"26_g5_laterano_chapelout","screenadapt":"coverall","id":557},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":558},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_351_1#4$1","id":559},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安多恩","text":"帕蒂亚，你真的要和我一起走吗？","id":560,"figure":"avg_4036_forcer_1#3$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_357_1#2$1","id":561},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"帕蒂亚","text":"当然。","id":562,"figure":"avg_npc_357_1#2$1"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_351_1#7$1","id":563},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安多恩","text":"其实我觉得，说不定你可以留在拉特兰。","id":564,"figure":"avg_npc_357_1#2$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_357_1#1$1","id":565},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"帕蒂亚","text":"拉特兰没有我的目标。","id":566,"figure":"avg_npc_357_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_357_1#4$1","id":567},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"帕蒂亚","text":"......？","id":568,"figure":"avg_npc_357_1#4$1"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_351_1#3$1","id":569},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安多恩","text":"怎么了，帕蒂亚？","id":570,"figure":"avg_npc_357_1#4$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_357_1#2$1","id":571},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"帕蒂亚","text":"......不，没什么，是我冒昧了。","id":572,"figure":"avg_npc_357_1#2$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_357_1#4$1","id":573},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"帕蒂亚","text":"只是......您......您是在笑吗？","id":574,"figure":"avg_npc_357_1#4$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_357_1#4$1","id":575},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"帕蒂亚","text":"不，我不是说您平时......但好像，不太一样？","id":576,"figure":"avg_npc_357_1#4$1"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_351_1#3$1","id":577},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安多恩","text":"只是......","id":578,"figure":"avg_npc_357_1#4$1"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_351_1#2$1","id":579},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安多恩","text":"长久以来，我以为我们于荒野中踽踽独行......这是我的不成熟和自以为是。","id":580,"figure":"avg_npc_357_1#4$1"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_351_1#1$1","id":581},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安多恩","text":"帕蒂亚，那天，你听到那位老人的演讲了吗？","id":582,"figure":"avg_npc_357_1#4$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_357_1#7$1","id":583},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"帕蒂亚","text":"......醒过来的时候，刚好听到后面一半，全城的广播都在放......很吵。","id":584,"figure":"avg_npc_357_1#7$1"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_351_1#6$1","id":585},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安多恩","text":"伊万杰利斯塔，拥有牺牲与团结美德的圣徒......也许，他比之前使用这个名字的十人，走得更远。","id":586,"figure":"avg_npc_357_1#7$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安多恩","text":"真是宏大又易碎的愿景。","id":587,"figure":"avg_npc_357_1#7$1"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_351_1#7$1","id":588},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安多恩","text":"但我愿奉上祝福......","id":589,"figure":"avg_npc_357_1#7$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_357_1#4$1","id":590},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"帕蒂亚","text":"......那天，您到底知晓了什么？","id":591,"figure":"avg_npc_357_1#4$1"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_351_1#8$1","id":592},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安多恩","text":"不重要了，帕蒂亚，不那么重要。","id":593,"figure":"avg_npc_357_1#4$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安多恩","text":"即使道路的尽头没有奖赏，前行本身就是举火。我亦当向前。","id":594,"figure":"avg_npc_357_1#4$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安多恩","text":"我们所做的一切，不为交易恩赐，不为换取垂怜，我们依仗自己坚信的事物行路，是因为......","id":595,"figure":"avg_npc_357_1#4$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安多恩","text":"这是唯一有尊严的生活。不是吗？","id":596,"figure":"avg_npc_357_1#4$1"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_364_1#1$1","id":597},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"罗塞菈","text":"先导，我们该出发了，得赶在太阳落山之前。","id":598,"figure":"avg_npc_357_1#4$1"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_351_1#7$1","id":599},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安多恩","text":"走吧，兄弟姐妹们。","id":600,"figure":"avg_npc_357_1#4$1"},{"type":"dialog","id":601},{"type":"character","id":602},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0.5","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":603},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"混血的女孩看到领头的男人迈出脚步。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":604},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"夕阳正缓缓落下，重叠了他头顶的光环。宛若冠冕。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":605},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"她想起小时候听过的圣徒故事......她想起妈妈郑重说出的那个词。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":606},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"她并不十分明白这个词具体的意义，或隐含的象征。它只是突然出现了，落在远处那个身影上。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":607},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"“殉道者”。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":608},{"type":"Subtitle","id":609},{"type":"Dialog","id":610},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":611},{"type":"character","id":612},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":613},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":614},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4036_forcer_1#8$1","id":615},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"艾泽尔","text":"塞茜莉亚，你在看什么？","id":616,"figure":"avg_npc_357_1#4$1"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_352_1#11$1","id":617},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞茜莉亚","text":"不，什么都没有。","id":618,"figure":"avg_npc_357_1#4$1"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_352_1#10$1","id":619},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞茜莉亚","text":"落日真美呀。","id":620,"figure":"avg_npc_357_1#4$1"},{"type":"dialog","id":621},{"type":"character","id":622},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0.5","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":623},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"女孩慢慢环顾四周，花田、教堂，远处的钟楼与圣像。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":624},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"最后，她紧紧握住年轻萨科塔的手，两人向远方走去。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":625},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"她走得很慢，但没有回头。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":626},{"type":"Subtitle","id":627},{"type":"Dialog","id":628},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"5","id":629},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"5","block":"true","id":630},{"type":"Dialog","id":631},{"type":"Character","id":632},{"type":"Image","id":633}],"characters":["休露丝","尤卡坦","艾泽尔","莫斯提马","菲亚梅塔","薇尔丽芙","蕾缪安","奥伦","费德里科","塞茜莉亚","里凯莱","修士","安多恩","帕蒂亚","罗塞菈"]}